{"type": "article", "id": 29228, "title": "像织物的灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-06T22:51:53Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160706213601jYs2fmTSEpqF5tQ9.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://mmozolewska.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Malgorzata Mozolewska</a> 以大自然中蝴蝶的翅膀和鸟儿的羽翼作为灵感，推出了 <a href=\"http://mmozolewska.com/projects/eye-of-the-light-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eye of the light</a> 灯具系列，灯罩部分看起来就像是一片片在风中飘扬的银色织物。Mozolewska 希望通过这个系列探索金属会如何呈现不同功能的家饰，轻盈多变的造型让 Eye of the light 能够呈现出不一样的光照效果，它既可以是吸睛的灯具，不亮灯时又能作为优雅的室内装饰品。Eye of the light 分为台灯、吊灯和落地灯三款，所有灯具都由来自波兰的工匠手工制成。这是它的<a href=\"http://shop.mmozolewska.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，价格从 525 到 2460 欧元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706220526pI2vASxZ4OUB1LNy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706220526P1RncNq8Z5sbzkVu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.100000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706220528aNRJgsOB4TqlWZG0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.910000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706220526304RrQgeLo1K8aSZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}